data.name: HelpInfo.Text
data.value:
In order to level up you kill enemies by walking into them. use the num pad or arrow keys to move. You cannot move diagonally.
Strength makes your regular attacks stronger. Dexterity gives you the chance to dodge attacks. Constitution gives you damage reduction on all attacks. Wisdom gives you more points when you level to increase stats. Intelligence increases your skill damage. Luck increases the amount of loot that you find. Charisma increases the chance to cause enemies to flee.
'p' or 't' picks up items. 'i' shows your inventory. 'h' or '?' shows and hides this help. '5' on the num pad waits a turn and allows you to heal 1 HP & WP. '1' is your primary skill '2' is your secondary skill '3' is your support skill '>' goes down stairs. 'f1' shows the high scores. 'f2' shows your character stats. 'f3' shows or hides the activity log. 'f4' exits game and restarts character creation.
<Press 'h' or '?' to hide this help>
